    <p>20/OWIGBOGU <a href="https://devdilettante.com/tags/rt">#rt</a>-flickr-worldwide-average-colour flickr ids e.g. 53733918346 are greater than ruby‚Äôs maximum integer value so the sort method fails if you are sorting using flickr‚Äôs ids converted to integers.:</p>

    <p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">53733918346 &gt; 2147483647 =&gt; true</code>
Solution: sort using a string I guess :-) !?!?</p>
